 \"relation\", \"from\": 3568, \"to\": 3576}, {\"ngram\": \"story prioritisation\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I think that's not surprising, and in fact, is much more responsive to the way in which people expect new services to be delivered.\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 3646, \"to\": 3650}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 3679, \"to\": 3686}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3696, \"to\": 3702}, {\"ngram\": \"new services\", \"from\": 3710, \"to\": 3722}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I make no apology for the fact I think news should be prioritised appropriately.\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no apology\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3767}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 3772, \"to\": 3780}, {\"ngram\": \"news\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sorry if that's unsatisfying.\\\"\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It follows ABC's star presenters Paul Barry and Laura Tingle recently becoming the subject of full throttled rebukes for insinuating the criticism of Kamala Harris was rooted in her gender and heritage and labelling Opposition Leader Peter Dutton \\\"dangerous\\\" while called Australia a racist country, respectively.\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 4178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3876, \"end\": 3879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999992364792, \"rank\": 7.633149884376711e-10, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 3903, \"end\": 3908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barry_Gibb\", \"score\": 0.9999998925559397, \"rank\": 1.0605807158522696e-07